{"tid":1294381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下星期繼續非港島區?","createTime":"2019-07-07T18:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T09:30:38.000Z","uid":75040,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c0b67d8d39d9f3bda659400410c35c520bf6d9","tid":1294381,"uid":75040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"見今晚大家都好嬲，隔離post話下次要勇武，要討論下一步行動<br />\n發夢下次就係勇武<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/QxDvMU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/QxDvMU</a><br />\n但係個人認為勇武都要有個目標<br />\n例如政總，立會(71)之類<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺上水/沙田會唔會事倍功半? 又被包圍然後敗退<br />\n因為未必set到物資站<br />\n無物資-&gt;捱打甚至被拉(唔係住嗰區嘅人未必熟路，大家應該熟金鐘啲路多啲)<br />\n<br />\n依家係想喺各區繼續宣傳，分散啲狗，遍地開花<br />\n抑或係下星期對準返政權一次先?<br />\n討論下一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f735553dd1cbed9ac8ab49efd1bcb2c4e3de8ec","tid":1294381,"uid":75040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32cb616ca1e1b31361657e36502e7b8ae734fe3","tid":1294381,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"去番維記好似好d"},{"pid":"9ac743fcdbc6cbc20b7d20122aa7ea1fb14bc097","tid":1294381,"uid":75040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ae30067e941ae2ced88380654947f792815b58","tid":1294381,"uid":151256,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:44:01.000Z","msg":"一星期地區 一星期全港？大家有得抖吓氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980cfd319d66dd959